Rockseeker took more damage, but this time, he felt the pain searing 
in him. The surge was ending, and it was time to go. He switched his 
guns and fired his dual gun at Hydras and his Radiant at Sharpclaw, 
then jumped into the air and transformed. He had to get away before 
it ended!
